xt-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 0 0 24px 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;匈牙利大选&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;前美国大使谈为何欧尔班的时代到了&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;周日，总理欧尔班·维克多 (Viktor Orbán) 的失败开启了匈牙利政治的新时代。这一变化对国家的“非自由”民主、欧盟和全球极右民粹主义运动意味着什么？美国前大使戴维·普莱斯曼 (David Pressman) 与彭博社坐下来进行解释。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;收听播客&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/u2y7V2oqM_zEitm8ZmKPewQx9PWzu4LVbFQV6Gb-m-T7Mn0Hz1s6s5BAQEERTCPq4OnxsLMFFXQI-j02-M_1fQ1xAUd7i0UfGRIIp-_-nfFlU34R7knrR3JIK7MwHHiy-DeDCJO6uLeskrm9uHk38t2AhiNvb4IeHge6r28nsT9NGVfTzypyfKZ8tbRLF2-IsCPFJeUrnWcmEdOc_zopUqQ0HvKWydkqwg58dtN_YMeGGQ3HJEcNkdFjmIo40VB4k5S9bxuwgeMEjfOeZItCt3qwp8TKcXQYMbbX3jw6LVVjFzpL-NWgyQJm7lWLe0ISn3IxucTm5tSWsOiGFXp1WNFB1GSPWpKa5oVUmwUTn5iwbKgwHchf71TqJMzsUuzvsjQ7xFim9NpISxuL4LZKrvI/K7EWADgBa7W6Ei99sEr21w-RE85e65Yb/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i55l7Jx3dlCc/v1/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Revelers are seen in the streets of Budapest, Hungary, on April 13. Thousands of people gathered after closing polls pointed to a victory for the Tisza opposition party, which will put an end to the 16-year rule by Fidesz. (Photo by Jaap Arriens/NurPhoto via Getty Images)" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none