so]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;自2月28日美国和以色列对伊朗发动袭击以来，全球能源市场一直处于疯狂状态，价格随着每一个新的头条新闻而上下波动。即使霍尔木兹海峡有望重新开放，世界各地的石油和天然气价格仍然上涨，我们开始看到对当地经济的影响，特别是亚洲的经济。本周，彭博社观点专栏作家戴维·菲克林 (David Fickling) 在《零》节目中解释了这些影响是什么，以及它们将如何在未来几十年重塑亚洲的能源系统。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;立即收听，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/_WbKuFbjjtsNMvleDgS1vfXZTRtMexmXds5vbVqsF4jhL6gAEEO0_lPCydY7yrozX4Klcx7jMtdwP6TSUJoKNp27oMLxBYq0rTmSIit4QAnNBMJIdtNQURmvW5OE6OOBnRdaJ8fQ30f_VfIf1v_EUkLjBKhNiRh9RmRsKvzD2OljLy4Zt-5d9OO8sqm2k7_uDQVbgDFOkCMGOx2ZcM7V6AMs9KqBFjkKAmnibh9habxSjXerqqkJza_ekmee3665VUVbLFUOPhqFYdWhy-IGOmndj3CItsfNRb1bb9AWNlPx_l5tNGabzJBsa-pAJFp48KNapg/yz51-2d8z2Thvk3NMqRe_bettG10DZWb/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/apRWA4rid8-aozj6lPQLk8QF3Udy8oTH25F0LL73lm5QF66F93Fs4r9t7CWVOg5xUijvwqrJ9prtn92PU-pbd9tHbHLKA9Qt-Qr6vqxqD4WQId5H0e81HkeOZfRtnO0f8vjKPw1m_IqjrXO7pvZBxPpVWQQTJznh_IhBjAjmpaZohac0AGgTDji7OkYrzc0OQRtilDX7WodDexGHKQHFSJ87zAJX2bxjy_z-wm9ME_x3BmuqOsld19lBAmG7FYb7hrChasIwqz_lCf9yn_gkn-GXOFcB8y8STXWzbJ90tBLlYOU1HZkrbwT_-TC5ukmuz-p-JG-tyZdcRGXHS6a3bt1bzK7W/NkYz3AzDzuwR7XLLHwdrdF1spAu_s0ZG/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Spotify&lt;/a&gt;或&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7vc_hEt4kpRIoEJ45s_dcq_Re8UMASqUhh7MPcZrrUIpI92jD67TpGZMUlejh45enHXHrXlRqgeJ8a101IFh2n8fr8vzZL4PHWnCSLBSIPUHBoMfiT9svE-2lwYVxGTpyzDURtcM4OBJhmqkUn0K46tjZ_suqqPl-RVKC_p7lymzmi8_QMeZPzAsVzoopcBvXpbSO9GDbXaEohikGwh4_A67-xufZgMUvoquLeMO2h0g4mPjzVmrOWkmEcKT1zgP3ttCc1hzekmHrTyiOYlzfSfKaIWibIHLampoIHDGy3O_38Ms-myC53rmJba6Vd1i2Zrx6zkwv1opgegE_d6mwBJI-z7Z/8iCr0T15w1193wHAb5BVK8CXW7KYeCH1/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt